Twenty One Pilots is a Grammy winning alternative rock emo duo from Columbus, Ohio
5:01 PM
They went mega viral in 2015 with the double platinum song Stressed Out, which is off their platinum album Blurryface
5:02 PM
Well known for their lore building and world building, they have acquired a massive following and an extremely devoted fan base @Deleted User
2
1
5:03 PM
Their 5th studio album, Clancy, was released last month, with the lead singles being Overcompensate, Next Semester, Backslide, and The Craving (Single Version)
5:03 PM
They span over a ton of genres, from pop, to rock, to emo, to ukulele ballads
5:05 PM
The lore is as follows
5:06 PM
So, there’s a fictional city named Dema on the continent of Trench. The city is ruled by nine bishops, who have taken a power and made a twisted and evil religion out of it
5:07 PM
The religion is called Vialism, and every citizen of Dema has to submit to it @Deleted User
5:09 PM
Vialism teaches that in order to achieve enlightenment, you must destroy yourself and eventually k*ll yourself. The power the Bishops have is this: they can control dead bodies and make them do their bidding
5:10 PM
The lead singer of tøp, Tyler Joseph, is a citizen of Dema named Clancy. He hates Vialism and has tried escaping the city multiple times, but every time he is captured by Nico, who is the leader of the Bishops and Vialism
5:12 PM
Eventually, Clancy does escape and is able to join the Banditos, who are a small group of rebels living in the wilderness that are trying to save the citizens of Dema from the bishops and Vialism
